  Stable for arm, wrt bug #448006

  03 Feb 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Cleanup due #333419

  31 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> networkmanager-0.9.6.4.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #448006

  28 Jan 2013; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
